Hence , RanBP2 and its partners emerge as critical modulators of neuronal HKI , <termsem="GO:0006007"> glucose catabolism </term> , energy <termsem="GO:0042592"> homeostasis </term> , and targets for <termsem="GO:0008152"> metabolic </term> , <termsem="GO:0007568"> aging </term> disorders and allied neuropathies .
